node.text:
What enabled you to share joy this past year? We talk with @chewy around 2020 and what it means to be a Joymaker! 🎁✨

GIVEAWAY // 
To enter: 
- Share a video of your cat
- Tag @Chewy + @cats_of_instagram 
- with the hashtag #ChewyJoymakers

We’ll feature the winner’s video on our Instagram and hook you and your kitty up with goodies!
#sponsored #catsofinstagram

node.text:
From @youngestoldcatlady: “Bunny loves her 🥛 milk so much I have to cut her off. Usually kittens will stop drinking when full, but bunny takes it to the limit 😂 There’s only so much stomach capacity in there Bunny! (Check a feeding chart to see how much they can eat at one feeding)

P.S. I am not pushing on the syringe. That speed is all Bunny! 🐰” #catsofinstagram
